itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson, Jared Taylor, and Dan Hollaway are joined by Jack Mandaville to recap the year 2020 in the last Drinkin’ Bros episode of the year. Dan and Jared give their favorite moments of 2020, Dan explains how Christmas wreaths are actually vaginas, Jared talks about his absurdly high stakes Super Bowl, and the gang learns what “Tunnel Buddies” means from James Wade and Cody Rogers.
